title: Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 62 - Off the Delta-8 (ft. Nick Colletti)
description:
Nick Colletti joins the show to talk about his stand up career, his Vine success, eat a bunch of snacks, and just chop it up with the fellas into some microphones.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/sonofaboydad
